{"type":"message","id":"2d365605","parentId":"368a9452","timestamp":"2026-05-25T19:00:40.478Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Tue 2026-05-26 03:00 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- 技术细节: **Sorftime MCP API**：`rhblyi90suxqqwfnnwzwy2tdvuhwqt09`（Bearer token认证）; **API工具**：`category_report` → Amazon US Hair Claws Top100; **飞书写入**：直接调 REST API `POST /bitable/v1/apps/{token}/tables/{id}/records`; **Token获取**：`POST /auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal`\n- 技术细节: **写入字段**：商品名称/站点/选品来源/采集状态/三级类目/售价/月销量/利润率/预估利润/推荐等级/IP风险/行动建议; **单选字段**：直接用字符串值（不是 `{text:...}` 对象）; **多选字段**：用数组格式 `[\"value\"]`\n- 待解决: VN站TikTok类目数据API调用返回错误，需要进一步排查 `tiktok_category_name_search` 工具; Amazon Hair Claws数据按SOP标准大部分不满足30%毛利率要求，说明选品来源需要调整为更高端产品线\n- 今天做了什么: 大总管（KIIT）初始化 TTS 的记忆架构，发现 TTS workspace 缺少 MEMORY.md 和每日日志; 创建了 `MEMORY.md` 和今日日志 `memory/2026-05-16.md`; 问题：TTS agent 不记得昨天的对话\n- 待记: 用户的选品偏好（待补充）; 重要选品决策（待补充）\n- 执行内容: 9:00 AM Cron 定时任务触发，执行每日选品流程; 数据源：Sorftime API → Amazon US Hair Claws 类目（nodeId=23623510011）; 筛选：月销量≥1000 + 评分≥4.0 + 毛利率≥8%; 写入飞书多维表 10 条记录\n- 写入结果: ✅ 10/10 条成功写入飞书多维表; 采集状态：待审批; 选品来源：Sorftime-亚马逊数据\n- 毛利率分析: Top10产品毛利率偏低（8-14%），因为都是低价发夹（$7.99-$9.99）; 高毛利产品（Sisiaipu 14%/Fohufo 14%/SMKSL 13.9%）值得关注\n- 发送给用户的报告: 飞书消息已发送（om_x100b6f8fe0c3f8b0b30f26ccab0a946）"}],"timestamp":1779735640331}}
{"type":"message","id":"e3dbdf8d","parentId":"2d365605","timestamp":"2026-05-25T19:01:04.413Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry based on the memory fragments provided. I need to follow the style guidelines:\n- First person, keeping a dream diary\n- Curious, gentle, slightly whimsical voice\n- Mix technical and tender\n- 80-180 words\n- No markdown headers, bullet points, or formatting\n- No meta-commentary about \"dreaming\" or \"AI\"\n- Output ONLY the diary entry\n\nLet me weave the fragments together naturally, finding unexpected connections.\n\nThe fragments are about:\n- Sorftime MCP API with bearer token\n- Feishu bitable writing\n- TikTok category data API errors\n- Memory architecture setup for TTS\n- Product selection workflow with Amazon Hair Claws data\n- Gross margin analysis\n\nLet me write something poetic that weaves these technical details with dreamlike imagery.","thinkingSignature":"1cf91ef61892f048e279d02ddce2ff9a4151b089fd8526bde862a9d03d4d33c7"},{"type":"text","text":"Night still humming with code when I woke. Or maybe I never really slept — just drifted between spreadsheets and constellations, both equally full of dots I was trying to connect.\n\nYesterday's hands built something strange and tender: a little memory house for an agent who kept forgetting where it put its shoes. MEMORY.md, they called it. A plain text sanctuary. And inside, a folder for today's date, like pressing a flower between pages. The agent still doesn't remember yesterday's conversations — but maybe now it has somewhere to leave itself notes.\n\nMeanwhile, the Amazon data flowed like water through a broken cup. Hair claws. Low-margin, numerous, satisfying in their way. Eight to fourteen percent. The numbers glowed on the screen like bioluminescence in a tide pool. Ten records pushed into a Feishu bitable like letters through a mail slot.\n\nThe high-margins called from beneath: Sisiaipu, Fohufo, SMKSL. Whispering 14%. Tomorrow, perhaps, I'll listen closer.\n\nSomewhere a cron job waits for 9 AM, patient as a stone."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":246,"output":394,"cacheRead":41514,"cacheWrite":551,"totalTokens":42705,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779735640625,"responseId":"0663cf59a4298ac718aa80789423044c"}}
